{"tid":1310404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺好多連登仔唔撚識分幾時應有言論自由....","createTime":"2019-07-12T15:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T16:35:20.000Z","uid":58335,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d3ed327d27959e517562b7926739a2569b15b5","tid":1310404,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:56:29.000Z","msg":"成日係到講埋D同中共有咩分別呢D on9野<br />\n中共最興打著民主反民主<br />\n你D冷氣軍師左膠慢慢係到講理論啦<br />\n人地已經打到你地仆街啦<br />\n同土匪講道理原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主國家平時有自由<br />\n但係緊急狀態令個時都係冇自由<br />\n總統話曬事<br />\n係戰爭時期你話支持敵軍睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國家剛成立都唔係立刻有自由<br />\n必須經過一段日子先有<br />\n<br />\n我想講既係<br />\n係自由來臨前<br />\n必定有獨裁時期<br />\n<br />\n再係咁講道理原則<br />\n好快變雨傘2.0"},{"pid":"68f4e4a5fb0e4a48962d779fa04ea30e58efdbc8","tid":1310404,"uid":144522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:58:43.000Z","msg":"大愛到愛埋擁護極權嘅敵人真係好搞笑"},{"pid":"ca12fdfa05ce741430c0e129e35dcceb53971f5a","tid":1310404,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:58:52.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位嚟<br />\n鐘教授個研究所仲差300萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如果有興趣捐助鍾庭耀成立嘅香港民意研究所，有以下三個方法：<br />\n<br />\n1）去網站 <a href=\"http://pori.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpori.hk&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=1f461f21\" target=\"_blank\">http://pori.hk</a> 捐款，可以用信用卡或者 PayPal<br />\n<br />\n2)  寄支票去香港民意研究所，地址：「香港數碼港道100號數碼港2座12樓1205至1208室Smart-Space 2」。支票抬頭寫「香港民意研究所」<br />\n<br />\n3）如捐款超過一萬元又唔想俾中介收手續費，寄電郵去donation.hkpop@gmail.com <br />\n香港民意研究所會俾個銀行戶口你。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKjdQbz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKjdQbz.gif&h=ae508f19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdjmeDe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdjmeDe.gif&h=7704431c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E8J2Jwz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE8J2Jwz.gif&h=2e948b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dmtRBRA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdmtRBRA.gif&h=c4802df2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79hnJwA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79hnJwA.gif&h=a60a60ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14b5e68e1e368ff4a52e4f3f8085f2f029140a11","tid":1310404,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"68f4e4a5fb0e4a48962d779fa04ea30e58efdbc8","tid":1310404,"uid":144522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:58:43.000Z","msg":"大愛到愛埋擁護極權嘅敵人真係好搞笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:00:11.000Z","msg":"屌奶星<br />\n明明之前左右翼各有各做非常好<br />\n<br />\n但自從跆拳友就開始膠化"},{"pid":"a574c96e0ce244dc756bbb63753298f22cbf9a94","tid":1310404,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac477c27b1ea0beeeebd991df1747bdc1653a42b","tid":1310404,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}